Trichomyia maldonadoi (Vargas)
, 1953 : 128 , plate III, figs. 8–11 (as
Eubonetia
). Type­locality: Mexico , Chiapas, Palenque, margins of the Chacamac River, light trap. A. Dampf, col. Holotype female (slide, Canada balsam): InDRE (PsT­ 87006 ). Additional references:
Satchell 1956
